    <p class="text-lg text-primary-900 dark:text-primary-100 leading-relaxed font-medium" data-gjs-type="text" data-gjs-name="text-content">
        This is a text block. You can edit this content to add your own text. The text will be styled with a nice readable font and proper spacing for optimal readability.
    </p>
</div> 